{"tid":2296054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本對共產黨加入CPTPP後會否遵守規則存疑","createTime":"2020-11-22T07:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T09:50:45.000Z","uid":21470,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9cfb8b7aa40565df36a55f586af18d9f5326c49f","tid":2296054,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:40:36.000Z","msg":"日方稱中國加入跨太平洋夥伴全面進步協定前提是守規則<br />\n<br />\n日本經濟再生擔當相西村康稔說，加入跨太平洋夥伴全面與進步關係協定的前提，是要遵守高水平規則。<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平日前表示，中方將積極考慮加入這項協定。<br />\n<br />\n西村康稔出席記者會時，對各國和地區關注協定，表示歡迎，強調協定的規則，比世界貿易組織更嚴格。<br />\n<br />\n他在回應中國有意加入時表示，必須確認是否準備好遵守自由公正的規則。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561298-20201122.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561298-20201122.htm&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItTyUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=7f4bbe8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561298-20201122.htm&h=a7af52b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561298-20201122.htm</a>"},{"pid":"efb4a386bb9615d72ba98b7877cd680e23ede713","tid":2296054,"uid":28628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:00:19.000Z","msg":"妓女比..........."},{"pid":"0c1856f6fb8f8be1d33e940a786c88880134b0de","tid":2296054,"uid":293677,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔需要存疑<br />\n百份之一千 肯定唔會遵守規則"},{"pid":"27aff8ab8de3f3677a76779a7b8c6444019ae321","tid":2296054,"uid":57675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:24:53.000Z","msg":"日本仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同叫